data.description: Your Home Awaits You!!! Location, Location, Location...Very Charming Home Located in the Temecula Valley, home of the Temecula Wine Country and Welcomes you to Redhawk Community near the Great Oak High and All that Temecula has to offer for Leisure and Entertainment.  This corner lot home also gives you the rear views of the Redhawk Golf Course.  The home features a 3 bedrooms with a loft that can be use as an office or another bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms, 2,386 square feet living Area, very low home owners association.  As you walk through the kitchen that opens to the living room, you will be greeted with an island, granite counter-tops, beautiful backsplash, plenty of cabinets for storage, walk-in pantry and more.  On the second floor, it features all three bedrooms with primary/master's bedroom and bathroom with a walk-in closet, separate shower and tub. All bedrooms has ceiling fans and carpet flooring.  The home is installed with luxury vinyl flooring throughout the downstairs and all the stairs and hallways including the step-up loft area upstairs.  An assumable loan at 2.875% may be possible, please inquire.  We look forward showcasing the home to you.
